	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinę</placeName> Satanam turbasse ecclesiam, <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerum</persName> cum <persName ref="p4744" cert="high">Paulo Fagio</persName> absolutos abireque iussos, <persName ref="p8374" cert="high">Hedionem</persName> etiam cum reliquis consensisse in [...].</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim, ieiunia mandata, festos dies instauratos ex literis <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Buceri</persName> leges, quas D. <persName type="auto_name">Musculo</persName> scribit.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quam miseri sumus homines et imbecilles [los?].</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verbum domini <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinę</placeName> nullas radices habuit; hoc debemus nostris peccatiset impęnitentię.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc debebat illis animum addi[di]sse, quo constantiores fuissent contra <persName ref="p18538" cert="high">Cęsaris</persName> edictum, quod audierunt et certo sciverunt <placeName type="auto_name">Saxonicas</placeName> civitates novum fędus cum rege Danię et multis principibus instituisse.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid sibi hoc vult?</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Mauricius dux Saxonię</persName> cum episcopo <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustano</placeName> missus ad Venetos, pulchri et probi legati.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam suspenderentur in itinere ad arborem aliquam praealtum, ut essent diu conspicui omnibus.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Schertlinus</persName> famulum habuit, quem miserat <placeName ref="l303" cert="high">Magdeburgum</placeName>, qui 2. Martii rediit; multa de constantia civitatum refert, ed dominus a <persName type="auto_name">Riffenberg</persName>, qui diu apud nos hęsit, iam agit in Brema civitate.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <placeName type="auto_name">Senensis</placeName> civitatis proditione fortasse melius nosti quam ego.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hęc paucis ad te; tabellio enim urget.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rescribe nacto otio, cur discesserit <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu commendasti <persName type="auto_name">Thomam</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Thomas Leymer/Argillanus; vgl. Basel, Matrikel II 54, Nr. 45 und Myc., 8.12.48.</note>, qui duxit abbatissam Seckingensem in uxorem; nam mira de te spargit, qui iam alterum superinduxit uxorem nobilem.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Timeo, ne coniiciatur in carcerem; est enim insignis nebulo, quem audio tibi commendatum a <persName ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconio</persName> nostro.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vehementer mihi dolet, si illum tibi suis in literis commendavit.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name">Abbatissa</placeName> honesta matrona adhuc constanter confitetur illud matrimonium semel cum nebulone contractum nec vult retractare.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Posset libere vivere sine custodia, si vellet abnegare.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil facio literas, quas fortassis habet ab episcopalibus extortas, quibus scribunt illum esse liberum nec posse propter votum semel datum ducere uxorem.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cur permittit <persName type="auto_name">Caesar</persName> in suo Interim?</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vide fallacias perditorum hominum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">5. Marcii 1549.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8171" cert="high">Bibliandrum</persName>, <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanum</persName> etc.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus quem nosti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An herren Heinrych Bullinger, lütpriester zuͦ Zurich, mynem lieben, gunstigen herren und frundt, zuͦ handen.</s>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zurich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
